{"tid":1394674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"減低水炮車傷害既＊盾＊（歡迎討論）","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T14:13:17.000Z","uid":277644,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eee08eb66a8eca55cdb328a3c820db5f8625aa08","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"首先希望大家睇左呢條片先，<br />\n我都係睇完呢條片有感而發。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vhaj2TXCh28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvhaj2TXCh28&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=22c8d279\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vhaj2TXCh28</a><br />\n我呢個post既目的唔係要鼓勵大家去擋水炮車，<br />\n因為最理想真係有咁遠走咁遠<br />\n只係假如有d突發事情，或者我以下既諗法可以有幫助，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">假設一</span>：水炮車定點射擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">假設二</span>：距離唔可以過近<br />\n<br />\n條片入面大家望到，基本上d軍人係用一己之力擋架水炮車，<br />\n假設一個人既體重係60kg，<br />\n我既目的就係要加大個mass，令到水炮車既威力減低<br />\n希望d圖晝得衰唔好見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owGywyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowGywyE.jpg&h=a00ce034&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n盾既設計如果理想既就流線形，唔得都唔緊要因為唔係最重點，<br />\n<strong>case1</strong> 假設水炮車射向盾既中心<br />\n因為我冇實質既data，只係知道5米內大約200磅力，<br />\n但假如去到20－30米外，相信威力會減低好多，<br />\n即使一個人擋唔住個沖力，兩個人應該擋得住。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>case2</strong> 假設水炮車射向盾既邊位<br />\n相對於比人直射，<br />\n因為另一邊有人施緊力，<br />\n理論上比人射緊果個人會好似張圖咁bend向另一邊，<br />\n理論上可以減少被直射既傷害，<br />\n同埋盾最好係正方形，<br />\n因為長方形會增加另一邊受既bending moment，<br />\n而圓形就可能會減少保護既範圍，<br />\n至於用咩物料或者個盾點樣整就要大家比idea，<br />\n而我覺得最理想係2個人拎盾，<br />\n因為太多人既話只會減低移動速度<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重申：呢個盾既目的，唔係要用黎同水炮車搏火</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只係當真係咁唔好彩，前排可能想拖延時間比後排走既方法</span><br />\n希望大家集思廣益"},{"pid":"eed75ccf0a07346616dce6ae466df988cca00257","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"推，希望大家睇下"},{"pid":"b0d33743c59061cde255aee249ba1dc67a0b44d0","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61a509cd35df1171553ffe67a38da9b12e261335","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27983ec715c325531950e1888e6596502d198fb3","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"808b956fd37c31c5ad4702594e34fe072600e8ea","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea34c6f9708846204e79e6add6abee2755706331","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ef77f717ccd422924e7cd610995e281ec05a806","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e427394322fcd8e1213ec4bb7fc636d19a843208","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d9e3db96158fff4f3ca95566114df9d9b93c69b","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc8c565e780ad1cdf1f4c3791cc7686180674fb3","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ed2cf3571ffb5c8513d0c0b72bc8d0bfa612344","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e455aa45e263fbde76b425566415d294365ef7c","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d79aca8d27c310ab0077cbead373b7fd3490c30","tid":1394674,"uid":277644,"like"