humbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CfvETp.png&h=a9371941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個諗法<br />\n其實無必要硬食啲水泡<br />\n可唔可以係用流線型既野卸走佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：非物理JJ"}]}